{"tid":1792962,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥稱她的個人資料網上被公開 實在令人擔憂","createTime":"2019-12-22T04:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T11:53:52.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"23b89068d29a46d0431413772b936efa3e07b8da","tid":1792962,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:42:22.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥在社交網站表示，她的個人資料近日被放上網上通訊群組，實在令人擔憂。她說，擔憂的是「起底」這種行為對社會的影響。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，過去幾個月，有人肆意對官員、警察以至所有與他們意見不合的人「起底」，甚至連他們的家人、小朋友都不放過，認為「起底」的目的就是消滅其他人的聲，但受害的是整個社會。<br />\n<br />\n她引用早前上訴庭處理一宗有關警察個人資料的案件時，法官的說法：「當許多人、目標群組或社會某個界別被恐嚇而噤聲，或因害怕被『起底』而不能公開、坦率地表達自己的意見、做他們想做的事或以他們渴望的方式生活時，社會會出現寒蟬效應。如果不遏止這個行為，它引發的不信任、恐懼和仇恨之火，很快會令公眾對法律和社會秩序的信心消失殆盡，從而導致我們的社會瓦解」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥呼籲大家警剔，不要被情緒影響是非對錯的判斷。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499038-20191222.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499038-20191222.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3Le6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=94dff5da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499038-20191222.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ea358bd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499038-20191222.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"630f40498e519b08aa258510bc9f8944dd535476","tid":1792962,"uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"做對了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c573c301c4f3d184b74bc471d639e18d2576b673","tid":1792962,"uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:43:57.000Z","msg":"最重要係佢老公係手足既角色被踢爆"},{"pid":"fa9c982e0fa1dbfb4f646145997f63986e45b14e","tid":1792962,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382b1596773c8719c0749e2dc6c0703eef98893c","tid":1792962,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8208e18fd8fb37366f9dafb1d07d53cb0858f4c2","tid":1792962,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c573c301c4f3d184b74bc471d639e18d2576b673","tid":1792962,"uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:43:57.000Z","msg":"最重要係佢老公係手足既角色被踢爆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:48:38.000Z","msg":"篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125f84fb89383df55c77a99ee50be77d96eb67f3","tid":1792962,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d00ef2949165fdb125aa1190ab038d7d6dd980","tid":1792962,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"燒埋689個起底網<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4168ae4c3c8398fb59bf80ed4ded4b2afbbea2a","tid":1792962,"uid":274772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:53:52.000Z","msg":"佢自己夠公開話係中紀委叫立送中條例<br />\n<br />\n為自己開脫責任出賣上級"}]}